title: Indie 69 July 2013 New Music Monthly
description:
Indie69 is a monthly collection/playlist of the latest music in many styles.
The number of tracks range from 69 to 100 or more.
There are a few older tracks sometimes, and an occasional dupe/repeat. But I
try to avoid those.
I pick the tracks not from personal taste as much as wanting the best
representative new tracks from as many genres as possible... with a few
remixes and mashups in there from time to time.

Enjoy, and for a file list, see above left and click on the number next to
the word "files".

Please seed for as long as possible....

@indie69

See you in August!


P.S. - Sorry it is late, I hope the quality makes up for it. I do my best
to avoid 128kbps files and do everything I can to find better quality versions.
